channel.title: How to enable currently disabled teleporting..?
channel.description: Erm well i'm using a Zaron's isle source, and it is set so that if you click no a teleport spell, it simply does .. nothing. No messages or anything. So obviously teleporting is disabled. I've spent ages playing around with all the spells and can't figure out how to re- enable them. Anyone help?

item.title: How to enable currently disabled teleporting..?
item.dc:creator: @xXH34DSH0TXx xXH34DSH0TXx
item.description:
@xXH34DSH0TXx wrote:

~R E B O R N~:

uhh search for if (s == "Varrock") then look around and see why you cant tele or make a command to tele to places.

Already have played around with all that, for hours, I said that >_>. And up until recently I have had teleing commands, but it basically ruins pking because they can get away with just a command… Anyone else have any better ideas? Or even if it does have to do with “varrock” tell me what could possibly be missing or something that is disabling my teleporting :S
